description: The Beauty of Darkness - The Beauty of Darkness series is a sequel to this. The difference here is that I lit it in complete darkness with a UV flashlight. I took photos with long shutter speeds and further illuminated more important areas, highlighting the main part of the flowers. It was the first time I photographed with a UV lamp, but I am sure this technique will continue. I don’t know what other objects I can try, but I can figure it out tomorrow. But a new world opened up for me, which impressed me.
